Package: msxtileforge
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, python3-tk, python3-pil, python3-numpy, python3-scipy, python3-platformdirs, python3-tqdm, ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}
Description: A tile and map editor for MSX2 game development.
 MSX Tile Forge is a comprehensive graphical application for creating and
 editing game assets for the MSX2 computer system. It allows users to
 manage color palettes, create 8x8 tiles with row-specific colors,
 build larger composite supertiles, and design full game maps.